header.gameNote: SUN BELT CONFERENCE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - FINAL

videos.description: D'Marcus Simonds drives and goes up through contact to get the hoop and harm.
videos.headline: Simonds gets strong and-1 for Georgia State

videos.description: Johnny Hamilton crashes the glass and goes up with two hands for the thunderous putback jam.
videos.headline: Hamilton throws down putback hammer for UT Arlington

videos.description: Malik Benlevi gets the ball and shoots a deep 3-pointer to extend the Panthers' lead to eight points.
videos.headline: Benlevi extends Georgia State's lead with long 3

videos.description: Georgia State's D'Marcus Simonds drives and elevates over UT Arlington's defense for a monster slam.
videos.headline: Simonds flies in for dunk in traffic

videos.description: Georgia State head coach Ron Hunter is ecstatic to be going back to the NCAA tournament, and even takes time to celebrate with his grandchild after winning the Sun Belt championship.
